net.shibboleth.utilities.java.support.component

Interface UnmodifiableComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Component
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AccessControlService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractReloadableService, BasicAccessControlService, DelegatingAccessControlService

    public interface UnmodifiableComponent
extends Component
    A marker interface for components that may be put in to an unmodifiable state and, if a modification is attempted afterwards, throws UnmodifiableComponentException.
